Package: selene
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rsync, mediainfo, ffmpeg | libav-tools, mplayer | mplayer2 | mpv, fdkaac, vorbis-tools, x264, lame, mkvtoolnix
Recommends: opus-tools, vpx-tools, libkate-tools, gpac, sox, x265
Description: Audio-video converter for Linux.
 Utility for converting audio and video files to OGG,OGV,
 MKV,MP4,WEBM,OPUS,AAC,FLAC,MP3 and WAV formats. Provides a simple
 GUI for converting files to popular formats with powerful command-line
 options for automated/unattended encoding.
